data.name: label7.Text
data.value:
Hi everyone, This is a message from the programmer of Gekijou.
I am including this "ad" Because I am desperately in need for a good telecommuting job.
For medical reasons I can not do a normal full time job. And I was hoping that someone out there would know a good telecommuting job and could recommend me for it. It must be low stress and have flexible hours. Must be a programming related job. It could even be part time or freelance. I could use Skype and email as my primary means of communication.
I hope that the fact that I could make this program shows that I am a talented programmer, I would also recommend seeing a couple of my other applications.
3dpl, The 3D programming language.
and Mobile RAD IDE which is a way to make Android apps and iOS apps directly on your Android device.
Once I can get a job (or monetize this app in some other way) so I can support myself I promise to take this "ad" off.
I am willing to put an ad for the company that hires me on here, or a facebook thumbs up or something like that! I want to express my gratitude!
Thanks in advanced!
Sincerely, Usmar A. Padow (amigojapan)
